This commissioned artwork captures a lighthearted yet gentle scene between two characters standing together in their school uniforms. One figure carries a playful presence with bunny ears and a relaxed stance, while the other stands with composed confidence, exuding calm charm. I really enjoyed bringing this moment to life, and I love how it carries both warmth and a touch of humor. I would love to hear your thoughts.
